cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.SI 

This paper proposes a new procedure for learning cost-sensitive SVM classifiers, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed algorithm is also extended to cost-sensitive learning with example dependent costs, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the connection between the proposed algorithm and ROC analysis, which is a topic related to social and information sciences (cs.SI).
